;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">/* 运行结果</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">多次运行的结果不唯一（尤其是线程数量较多的时候）</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">*/</span></span></code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>但是用户可以自己加锁，保证线程安全：</p>\n<div class=\"language-cpp line-numbers-mode\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"cpp\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\